		<h2 class="wpb_heading wpb_singleimage_heading">Handbook of Inpatient Glucose Management</h2>
		<figure class="wpb_wrapper vc_figure">
			<div class="vc_single_image-wrapper   vc_box_border_grey"><img width="662" height="504" src="https://www.cdi.org.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/HANDBOOK-OF-IN-PATIENT-GLUCOSE-MANAGEMENT-final12-feb.jpg" class="vc_single_image-img attachment-large" alt="Handbook of in-patient glucose management" srcset="https://www.cdi.org.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/HANDBOOK-OF-IN-PATIENT-GLUCOSE-MANAGEMENT-final12-feb.jpg 662w, https://www.cdi.org.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/HANDBOOK-OF-IN-PATIENT-GLUCOSE-MANAGEMENT-final12-feb-300x228.jpg 300w, https://www.cdi.org.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/HANDBOOK-OF-IN-PATIENT-GLUCOSE-MANAGEMENT-final12-feb-600x457.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 662px) 100vw, 662px" /></div>
		</figure>
	</div>
</div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container text-default vc_col-sm-6"><div class="vc_column-inner "><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 32px" ><span class="vc_empty_space_inner"></span></div>

	<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >
		<div class="wpb_wrapper">
			<p><span style="color: #333333; font-size: 18px;">This practical handbook authored and edited by doctors from the Chellaram Diabetes Institute, Pune, India is for trainee and practising doctors.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #333333; font-size: 18px;">The handbook covers all aspects of inpatient glucose management in the ward and critical illness settings. The handbook focusses on various scenarios of glucose management like patients undergoing surgery, on enteral or parenteral feeding and end-of-life diabetes care. Subcutaneous insulin and intravenous insulin infusion therapy have been explained along with practical guidelines for management of common glycemic emergencies.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #333333; font-size: 18px;">User friendly algorithms and protocols are explained using tables, flowcharts, diagrams and case studies.</span></p>
<p><a href="https://www.amazon.in/Handbook-Patient-Glucose-Management-Unnikkrishnan/dp/9381791902/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class=" wp-image-7304 aligncenter" src="https://www.cdi.org.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/AMZ-Button-300x113.png" alt="" width="250" height="94" srcset="https://www.cdi.org.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/AMZ-Button-300x113.png 300w, https://www.cdi.org.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/AMZ-Button.png 351w" sizes="(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px" /></a></p>

